# Global Safety

- Follow `prompt.md`, `cursor.md`, `SPEC.md`, and `task1.md` ... `task9.md` as source of truth.
- Never touch unrelated services or configs outside mapvideo scope.
- Critical: do not modify existing `maps.gyhyry.ru` nginx configs/certs/services.
- Critical: do not run nginx as a Docker service for this project.
- Use host nginx only for `80/443`; app services bind to `127.0.0.1:*`.
- Do not use destructive commands (`reset --hard`, force push, blanket deletes) unless explicitly requested.
- If unexpected external changes appear, stop and ask user before proceeding.
